title: Scallop
description: A close-up image of a scallop shell, showcasing its vibrant colors and ridged texture. The shell is primarily red and orange with white accents, resting on a sandy ocean floor surrounded by other marine elements.

title: Slug on a Leaf
description: A close-up image of a brown slug resting on a green leaf. The slug has a textured, ridged surface and is positioned near a hole in the leaf, suggesting it may have been feeding on it. The leaf is vibrant and shows droplets of water, indicating a fresh or moist environment.

title: Cross-section of a Shell
description: A cross-section of a shell showing a smooth, shiny interior with a dark central area and several small, round white objects, possibly pearls, embedded within.

title: Snail on Moss
description: A close-up image of a snail resting on a bed of green moss. The snail has a spiral shell that is brown and tan in color, with a smooth, slimy body extending from underneath the shell. The background features blurred green foliage, creating a natural and serene environment.

title: Simple Geometric Shape
description: A minimalist design featuring a white outline of a geometric shape on a black background. The shape resembles a corner or an L-like figure.
